    "base_url": "https://everyayah.com/data",
    "url_template": "{base_url}/{folder}/{surah:03d}{ayah:03d}.mp3",
    "notes": [
      "One MP3 per ayah. Single-ayah playback = one file; full-surah playback = files 001..N in sequence.",
      "surah and ayah are zero-padded to 3 digits, e.g. surah 2 ayah 286 -> 002286.mp3",
      "All folders below were verified to return HTTP 200 on 2026-06-19.",
      "Licensing: EveryAyah serves these freely and they are used widely, but no formal per-reciter license is published. Fine for personal scope; revisit before any public release (same posture as the non-commercial Tanzil translations)."
    ]
  },
